{
  "stem": "24259.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And my father and mother had gone out to procure to see that-- when they went into the ghetto, they gave certain valuables to various farmers in the area that they trusted.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And my father would periodically go out and take some things to give as payment, in a sense, or kind of show his appreciation to the farmers that hid us.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And this one evening, my mother and my father left me and my aunt hiding.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they went out to one of the farmers to get it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And a lot of times, I'm told my mother would just hide in the-- outside the barn somewhere, and my father would go in the house and so on.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And on the way back, they-- my father was going to go visit.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "He knew-- somehow, he found out where my mother's brothers were hiding, and he was going to go visit them.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And my mother said-- she was kind of nervous about it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "She said, gee, we left, you know, me with my aunt.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And she said, well, let's go visit them some other time.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And then they-- they did not go to visit the farm where my mother's brothers were hidden.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And that was the time that they were discovered and killed by the Germans.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "So through some fate, my parents did not go visit the family, and-- or they would have been killed right at that same time.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "So these are little things that kind of, for whatever reason they happened, miraculously enabled us to survive.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Shortly after that, again, through the conversations with the farmer that was hiding us.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
